text: Maynes may refer to: *Ben Jacques-Maynes (born 1978), American road bicycle racing cyclist from Watsonville, California *Dan Maynes-Aminzade (aka Monzy) is a Nerdcore hip-hop artist and software engineer at Google *Seaghan Maynes (1914–1998), Reuters correspondent, covered the Invasion of Normandy, the Reconstruction of Germany, and the 1948 Arab Israeli War
